{"id": 417, "genre": 1001, "title": "全民炒股，你在烦什么？", "description": "如果不是有勇无谋配资被强平，没有伤筋动骨大亏，盈亏浮动几千块天天大呼小叫刷存在感也真是蛮无聊的。", "record_count": 793, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606052121063yTN9OdX4c1UVtlg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-08T12:50:18Z", "options": [{"id": 3178, "content": "乘机学习股票股市金融知识，为抄底做好准备！", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137686}, {"id": 3179, "content": "全民炒股 烦的是我不在民里面……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 26306}, {"id": 3181, "content": "大家突然都成了爱国主义者", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3176, "content": "句句戳中我办公室老阿姨", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3186, "content": "我的1w亿明天入场救市", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234938ImnH7reTwJEWzoZa.jpg", "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 3183, "content": "从前的时光很慢，车、马、邮件都很慢；一生，只够爱一个人；一千点，可以跌一年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130994}, {"id": 3157, "content": "经济学家、评论家、阴谋论剖析家迭出，真想割他们一茬又一茬", "image": "img/option/option/2016060423493774icGok3qrEVmdy5.jpg", "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3158, "content": "等2800再进", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41487}, {"id": 3255, "content": "不會炒又在那裝B", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137194}, {"id": 3258, "content": "国家不会抛弃我的 国家会来救我的 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3263, "content": "有反弹的时候你不跑 要补仓  第二天分分钟教你做人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 41653}, {"id": 3266, "content": "我只是想要封面原图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 135619}, {"id": 3511, "content": "买哪个哪个跌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140980}, {"id": 6098, "content": "烦没钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149663}, {"id": 3188, "content": "转了点钱装股神装逼，现在没声音了，真好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3365, "content": "亲朋好友知道你炒股，开口就问买什么股票好，我只想说：中国中车你值得拥有（误）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3149, "content": "股市跌了就狂晒自己的绿色的衣服鞋子头绳青菜什么的，说“怪不得！！！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3150, "content": "总共买了两千块股票跌了几百块一直在大呼小叫喊跳楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 152, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3151, "content": "说自己的一个包/一辆车/一套房没了（关我屁事啊！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3152, "content": "自称社会主义接盘侠", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 14416, "content": "我在烦今天赚的钱如何从新放进去套牢", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 220251}, {"id": 3153, "content": "整天自称“共和国六十六年满仓为国护盘”，呵了个呵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3154, "content": "老板说给股民放两天安慰假但…只是说说而已", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 89896}, {"id": 3156, "content": "所有的饭局上都在聊股票。", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234937pNjn5HKqE6XlO3RQ.jpg", "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 3168, "content": "整天喊“救市大部队在哪里！”你不知道就是你吗。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 3169, "content": "没进的秀智商。。进了的秀智商下限。。人类啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 3170, "content": "根本不炒股的人被不想听的讨论包围了", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114642}, {"id": 3171, "content": "开户俩月就开始给人荐股做分析三句话不离股市", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116854}, {"id": 3172, "content": "所有的微信群都在聊股票", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 3173, "content": "心情不好了，朋友直接发给我一张绿头盘压惊（真朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 3184, "content": "社会主义股市搞不好 可以关掉嘛 邓小平说", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3185, "content": "我从没炒股过，你们的世界我不懂~~~", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3187, "content": "明明自己的股票天天跌停，还有人在朋友圈晒收益", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1696}, {"id": 3189, "content": "竟然相信为国接盘和国家队，太蠢了，一个个抄底抄在半山腰", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3194, "content": "股票投资三年，绝大部时间赚钱，就这段时间亏钱，就几乎被否定了，表示不服", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120486}, {"id": 3196, "content": "曾经在我的账户上停了一辆最新款兰博基尼。。我没有好好珍惜。。结果肖钢就开走了。。。开走的时候还叫李克强担保说过两天就还。。。打了好多次欠条。。最后。。。又借了我几次加油钱。。。人就不见了\u0014", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 3197, "content": "照这个趋势四天就可以全部停牌了，没有买卖就没有杀害。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 98345}, {"id": 3198, "content": "赚钱就跑", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137939}, {"id": 3200, "content": "以为自己是股票大跌的主力军，作为小散都不够格的路人甲，咱能不把自己看的辣么重要么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 123083}, {"id": 3208, "content": "中国股票越来越迷茫", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234800gc6YkLJ9m1BI7MzP.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138034}, {"id": 3209, "content": "我更想吐槽我妈把KONKA打成K口NKA：））", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234708uCM2pbOynTSmXZ5r.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115788}, {"id": 3276, "content": "猛跌猛涨特别不靠谱，最近绿得跟粽叶似的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138744}, {"id": 3282, "content": "不炒股的也再喊跳楼", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234708bCv5oBgqLITVZ2xA.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109839}, {"id": 5618, "content": "一群傻子比蠢的博弈游戏，都认为能超脱，结果发现自己只是傻子中的聪明人，结果还是傻子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148204}]}